@page "/"

<PageTitle>ShopFloor</PageTitle>

<h1>ShopFloor - ISA-95 Manufacturing Operations</h1>

<p>Welcome to ShopFloor, a manufacturing execution system built on Allors3 and the ISA-95 (IEC 62264) standard.</p>

<div class="row mt-4">
    <div class="col-md-4">
        <div class="card">
            <div class="card-body">
                <h5 class="card-title">Equipment</h5>
                <p class="card-text">Manage your equipment hierarchy from Enterprise down to Work Units. Configure equipment properties and map physical assets.</p>
                <a href="equipment" class="btn btn-primary">View Equipment</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-4">
        <div class="card">
            <div class="card-body">
                <h5 class="card-title">Maintenance</h5>
                <p class="card-text">Create and track maintenance job orders. Dispatch work, record completions, and track personnel and material actuals.</p>
                <a href="maintenance" class="btn btn-primary">View Maintenance</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-4">
        <div class="card">
            <div class="card-body">
                <h5 class="card-title">Personnel</h5>
                <p class="card-text">Manage personnel classes (roles) and individual persons. Assign qualifications and track who is available for work.</p>
                <a href="personnel" class="btn btn-primary">View Personnel</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
